WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 27=

00:02:28.460 --> 00:02:29.300 line:80%
For two hundred years,

00:02:29.810 --> 00:02:31.690 line:80%
the Demon Sect has plagued the martial world.

00:02:32.410 --> 00:02:34.140 line:80%
Thanks to our forebears of Beichen,

00:02:34.740 --> 00:02:35.620 line:80%
who upheld justice and

00:02:36.060 --> 00:02:37.140 line:80%
defended the righteous path,

00:02:37.860 --> 00:02:39.090 line:80%
peace has endured

00:02:39.410 --> 00:02:40.780 line:80%
despite countless perils.

00:02:41.740 --> 00:02:44.300 line:80%
With the blessing of the Three Pure Ones

00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:46.180 line:80%
and the spirits of our ancestors,

00:02:46.740 --> 00:02:47.970 line:80%
we, unworthy disciples,

00:02:48.490 --> 00:02:49.530 line:80%
have captured

00:02:49.860 --> 00:02:51.340 line:80%
the Demon Sect's leader,

00:02:52.020 --> 00:02:52.930 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:02:53.930 --> 00:02:56.370 line:80%
It is hereby decided that his meridians
be destroyed.

00:02:57.090 --> 00:02:57.930 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:02:59.300 --> 00:03:00.140 line:80%
from now on,

00:03:00.410 --> 00:03:01.650 line:80%
you may remain at Qingque Sect

00:03:02.090 --> 00:03:03.930 line:80%
to cultivate and recuperate.

00:03:04.740 --> 00:03:05.580 line:80%
No way.

00:03:05.970 --> 00:03:07.410 line:80%
Then what do you want?

00:03:11.410 --> 00:03:12.460 line:80%
Remove these shackles

00:03:13.690 --> 00:03:14.530 line:80%
and let me go.

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:16.020 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:03:17.210 --> 00:03:18.410 line:80%
kneel when you speak!

00:03:19.690 --> 00:03:21.060 line:80%
His injuries are too severe.

00:03:21.860 --> 00:03:22.700 line:80%
He cannot kneel.

00:03:26.090 --> 00:03:27.340 line:80%
Then make him crawl.

00:03:38.140 --> 00:03:39.900 line:80%
Lord Yang, as a sect leader,

00:03:39.900 --> 00:03:41.090 line:80%
have you no decorum?

00:03:41.090 --> 00:03:43.370 line:80%
You expect decorum when dealing with a demon?

00:03:43.370 --> 00:03:44.220 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:03:44.230 --> 00:03:45.100 line:80%
Enough.

00:03:45.580 --> 00:03:47.000 line:80%
Everyone, calm down.

00:03:47.620 --> 00:03:49.690 line:80%
Let Lord Qi preside.

00:03:50.580 --> 00:03:52.620 line:80%
Others need not interrupt.

00:04:01.300 --> 00:04:02.140 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:04:02.780 --> 00:04:04.300 line:80%
for the matter of Lord Wang alone,

00:04:05.060 --> 00:04:06.650 line:80%
you could be executed.

00:04:07.410 --> 00:04:08.250 line:80%
Now,

00:04:08.490 --> 00:04:10.020 line:80%
we spare your life and merely

00:04:10.370 --> 00:04:11.530 line:80%
destroy your meridians,

00:04:11.530 --> 00:04:13.370 line:80%
this is Beichen's mercy.

00:04:33.610 --> 00:04:34.900 line:80%
Standing by while others die,

00:04:37.020 --> 00:04:38.210 line:80%
abetting evil,

00:04:38.970 --> 00:04:40.500 line:80%
exterminating entire clans,

00:04:41.210 --> 00:04:42.650 line:80%
is that

00:04:42.650 --> 00:04:43.730 line:80%
your mercy?

00:04:44.140 --> 00:04:44.980 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:04:46.170 --> 00:04:47.900 line:80%
You killed Lord Wang and now

00:04:48.700 --> 00:04:49.970 line:80%
dare slander his name!

00:04:50.530 --> 00:04:51.410 line:80%
That's not true!

00:04:53.090 --> 00:04:53.940 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:53.940 --> 00:04:54.850 line:80%
the decision is made.

00:04:54.850 --> 00:04:55.690 line:80%
Do not interfere.

00:04:56.210 --> 00:04:57.050 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:57.380 --> 00:04:59.050 line:80%
he is the Demon Sect's leader.

00:04:59.730 --> 00:05:01.090 line:80%
If we do not cripple him today,

00:05:01.460 --> 00:05:03.210 line:80%
once he regains strength

00:05:03.580 --> 00:05:06.170 line:80%
he will be a grave threat to the Six Sects.

00:05:07.780 --> 00:05:08.620 line:80%
Carry out the sentence.

00:05:55.650 --> 00:05:56.490 line:80%
Wait.

00:05:57.380 --> 00:05:58.220 line:80%
Master,

00:05:58.360 --> 00:05:59.220 line:80%
does there

00:05:59.220 --> 00:06:00.650 line:80%
truly remain no other path?

00:06:01.090 --> 00:06:01.970 line:80%
This is

00:06:01.970 --> 00:06:03.940 line:80%
the only way to spare his life.

00:06:05.050 --> 00:06:05.890 line:80%
Proceed.

00:06:45.700 --> 00:06:46.540 line:80%
Master,

00:06:46.970 --> 00:06:48.290 line:80%
if you cripple him today,

00:06:49.610 --> 00:06:51.020 line:80%
I will not live.

00:06:53.050 --> 00:06:54.050 line:80%
- Zhao!
- Zhao!

00:06:54.050 --> 00:06:54.890 line:80%
Zhao!

00:07:02.290 --> 00:07:03.210 line:80%
Zhao!

00:07:04.350 --> 00:07:05.200 line:80%
Zhao!

00:07:05.290 --> 00:07:06.130 line:80%
Zhao!

00:07:10.050 --> 00:07:10.900 line:80%
Father!

00:07:13.790 --> 00:07:14.650 line:80%
Master!

00:07:14.650 --> 00:07:15.490 line:80%
Father!

00:07:21.170 --> 00:07:22.210 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:07:52.850 --> 00:07:54.380 line:80%
You unfilial disgrace!

00:08:11.090 --> 00:08:11.930 line:80%
Zhao!

00:08:14.060 --> 00:08:14.930 line:80%
Xiaofeng!

00:08:15.050 --> 00:08:15.890 line:80%
Pingchun.

00:08:29.050 --> 00:08:29.890 line:80%
How could she...

00:08:30.340 --> 00:08:31.460 line:80%
It's Drizzle Numbing Powder.

00:08:33.650 --> 00:08:34.490 line:80%
The tea?

00:08:35.170 --> 00:08:36.010 line:80%
Yes.

00:08:36.900 --> 00:08:37.860 line:80%
Foolish child.

00:09:06.220 --> 00:09:07.220 line:80%
Zhao.

00:09:07.220 --> 00:09:08.650 line:80%
Don't make another mistake.

00:09:08.650 --> 00:09:09.930 line:80%
You can still turn back.

00:09:10.530 --> 00:09:11.650 line:80%
There is no turning back.

00:09:13.780 --> 00:09:14.620 line:80%
Zhao.

00:09:29.100 --> 00:09:30.140 line:80%
Dad, what are you doing?

00:09:30.140 --> 00:09:31.530 line:80%
Do you still want to marry Zhao?

00:09:31.530 --> 00:09:32.810 line:80%
Then listen to me.

00:09:34.930 --> 00:09:36.220 line:80%
If Mu escapes, so be it.

00:09:36.220 --> 00:09:37.890 line:80%
We must do nothing now.

00:09:37.890 --> 00:09:38.730 line:80%
Come on.

00:09:38.740 --> 00:09:40.640 line:80%
Pretend the Chaos Needles are acting up

00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:41.500 line:80%
and you can't move.

00:09:41.500 --> 00:09:42.340 line:80%
Come on!

00:09:51.620 --> 00:09:53.220 line:80%
Son, listen to me.

00:09:53.690 --> 00:09:55.650 line:80%
If you go out now, will you help her save him

00:09:55.650 --> 00:09:56.620 line:80%
or stop her?

00:09:56.620 --> 00:09:58.500 line:80%
You must calm down.

00:09:58.500 --> 00:09:59.340 line:80%
Stay.

00:10:13.290 --> 00:10:14.290 line:80%
MoonLake?

00:10:16.170 --> 00:10:17.010 line:80%
Let's break off the engagement.

00:10:18.220 --> 00:10:19.530 line:80%
- Aunt once said,
- Pingshu.

00:10:19.530 --> 00:10:21.100 line:80%
loving someone is not wrong,

00:10:21.810 --> 00:10:23.500 line:80%
but if they don't love you the same way,

00:10:24.650 --> 00:10:26.020 line:80%
don't hold on too long.

00:10:40.140 --> 00:10:40.980 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:10:41.530 --> 00:10:42.450 line:80%
Uncle Zhou.

00:10:54.140 --> 00:10:55.410 line:80%
Don't think you can escape!

00:10:55.410 --> 00:10:57.980 line:80%
Even if he flees, he won't survive.

00:11:19.220 --> 00:11:20.060 line:80%
My son!

00:11:24.050 --> 00:11:24.890 line:80%
Zhao!

00:11:37.290 --> 00:11:38.130 line:80%
Release the arrows!

00:11:38.450 --> 00:11:39.530 line:80%
- No, stop!
- Stop!

00:11:39.530 --> 00:11:40.370 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:11:40.930 --> 00:11:41.770 line:80%
Stop!

00:11:44.690 --> 00:11:45.690 line:80%
- Stop!
- Don't do it!

00:11:45.690 --> 00:11:46.930 line:80%
- Stop!
- Stop!

00:11:46.930 --> 00:11:47.770 line:80%
Stop!

00:11:49.740 --> 00:11:51.220 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:11:58.330 --> 00:11:59.860 line:80%
Xiaofeng. Xiaofeng.

00:11:59.980 --> 00:12:00.820 line:80%
Xiaofeng!

00:12:01.810 --> 00:12:02.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:12:02.740 --> 00:12:04.650 line:80%
you heartless girl!

00:12:04.650 --> 00:12:06.860 line:80%
If you wanted to free him, fine...

00:12:06.860 --> 00:12:08.330 line:80%
but why leave as well?

00:12:13.930 --> 00:12:14.770 line:80%
Chief,

00:12:21.380 --> 00:12:22.450 line:80%
Cai Zhao

00:12:22.450 --> 00:12:23.500 line:80%
colluded with the Demon Sect,

00:12:23.500 --> 00:12:24.740 line:80%
betrayed her master and ancestors, and

00:12:24.740 --> 00:12:25.740 line:80%
gravely injured fellow disciples.

00:12:25.740 --> 00:12:26.930 line:80%
Her crimes are unforgivable.

00:12:26.930 --> 00:12:27.980 line:80%
Issue a pursuit order

00:12:27.980 --> 00:12:29.220 line:80%
to the world at once.

00:12:29.220 --> 00:12:30.690 line:80%
Let all righteous sects

00:12:30.690 --> 00:12:31.980 line:80%
hunt down and capture

00:12:32.900 --> 00:12:34.530 line:80%
Mu Qingyan

00:12:34.530 --> 00:12:35.980 line:80%
and the traitor

00:12:36.780 --> 00:12:37.620 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:14:04.650 --> 00:14:05.490 line:80%
Bear with it.

00:14:12.490 --> 00:14:14.220 line:80%
♪In days gone by♪

00:14:14.530 --> 00:14:16.080 line:80%
♪Willows swayed gently♪

00:14:16.380 --> 00:14:19.130 line:80%
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

00:14:20.100 --> 00:14:21.290 line:80%
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

00:14:21.300 --> 00:14:22.770 line:80%
♪A fleeting glance♪

00:14:22.940 --> 00:14:23.850 line:80%
♪And then♪

00:14:23.860 --> 00:14:26.810 line:80%
♪Love consumed me♪

00:14:27.620 --> 00:14:29.170 line:80%
♪Now I think of you♪

00:14:29.570 --> 00:14:31.210 line:80%
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

00:14:31.470 --> 00:14:32.810 line:80%
♪Alas, we parted♪

00:14:32.820 --> 00:14:35.010 line:80%
♪Longing for your return♪

00:14:35.140 --> 00:14:36.090 line:80%
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

00:14:36.100 --> 00:14:37.570 line:80%
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

00:14:37.580 --> 00:14:38.610 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:14:38.620 --> 00:14:40.850 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:14:42.950 --> 00:14:43.810 line:80%
Zhao,

00:14:43.930 --> 00:14:44.770 line:80%
are you all right?

00:14:45.810 --> 00:14:46.900 line:80%
Let me apply some medicine.

00:14:49.050 --> 00:14:51.770 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:14:52.030 --> 00:14:55.970 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:14:56.690 --> 00:14:59.220 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:03.750 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:15:04.050 --> 00:15:06.630 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:15:07.010 --> 00:15:11.350 line:80%
♪Tears are like pearls♪

00:15:27.530 --> 00:15:29.140 line:80%
♪Now I think of you♪

00:15:29.470 --> 00:15:31.270 line:80%
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

00:15:31.450 --> 00:15:32.690 line:80%
♪Alas, we parted♪

00:15:32.690 --> 00:15:35.150 line:80%
♪Longing for your return♪

00:15:35.150 --> 00:15:37.510 line:80%
♪Moon waxes and wanes, letters can't convey
my thoughts♪

00:15:37.510 --> 00:15:38.420 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:15:38.420 --> 00:15:41.220 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:15:42.170 --> 00:15:45.510 line:80%
♪Wedding candles glow, by the window we share♪

00:15:45.510 --> 00:15:47.950 line:80%
♪Do you still remember♪

00:15:49.650 --> 00:15:52.020 line:80%
♪A single light skiff drifting away?♪

00:15:52.020 --> 00:15:56.710 line:80%
♪Where my brush falls, it's you♪

00:15:57.150 --> 00:15:58.990 line:80%
♪Distant hills so clear♪

00:15:59.500 --> 00:16:04.170 line:80%
♪Looking back, all worldly vanities disappear♪

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:08.770 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:16:08.770 --> 00:16:13.550 line:80%
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

00:16:13.550 --> 00:16:16.030 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:20.840 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:16:21.010 --> 00:16:23.910 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:16:23.910 --> 00:16:28.430 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:16:28.560 --> 00:16:31.050 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:16:31.390 --> 00:16:36.500 line:80%
♪Tears are like pearls♪

00:16:39.760 --> 00:16:42.230 line:80%
♪Falling blossoms so fair♪

00:16:42.530 --> 00:16:44.700 line:80%
♪Endless love beyond compare♪

00:16:44.780 --> 00:16:45.620 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:16:46.900 --> 00:16:47.740 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:16:48.290 --> 00:16:49.530 line:80%
why are your injuries worsening?

00:16:51.650 --> 00:16:52.620 line:80%
The needles...

00:16:53.500 --> 00:16:54.930 line:80%
It's the execution needles.

00:17:00.780 --> 00:17:01.650 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:17:16.530 --> 00:17:17.890 line:80%
(I've already infused him
with internal energy,)

00:17:18.330 --> 00:17:20.020 line:80%
(why is he still alternating between chills
and heat?)

00:17:29.570 --> 00:17:32.700 line:80%
Even if he flees, he won't survive.

00:17:39.020 --> 00:17:40.290 line:80%
This poison is no weaker

00:17:40.290 --> 00:17:42.660 line:80%
than Taichu Temple's Cold Spirit Powder.

00:17:43.290 --> 00:17:44.130 line:80%
What is the Cold Spirit Powder?

00:17:44.530 --> 00:17:46.130 line:80%
Taichu Temple's secret poison.

00:17:46.890 --> 00:17:49.780 line:80%
They say it traps you between searing heat
and frozen agony.

00:17:50.290 --> 00:17:51.810 line:80%
Ten days, and you're dead.

00:17:52.850 --> 00:17:53.690 line:80%
But

00:17:53.690 --> 00:17:55.090 line:80%
I already made an antidote.

00:17:55.570 --> 00:17:57.570 line:80%
Snow lotus from the extreme coldness

00:17:58.020 --> 00:17:59.220 line:80%
can cure it.

00:18:32.130 --> 00:18:33.090 line:80%
The Lord's wounds

00:18:33.940 --> 00:18:35.020 line:80%
look grave,

00:18:35.330 --> 00:18:36.330 line:80%
but they're not life-threatening.

00:18:36.980 --> 00:18:38.370 line:80%
Zhao held back.

00:18:38.780 --> 00:18:39.850 line:80%
Held back?

00:18:40.610 --> 00:18:41.810 line:80%
She schemed against the Lord,

00:18:42.130 --> 00:18:43.220 line:80%
crippled Lord Zhou,

00:18:43.500 --> 00:18:44.370 line:80%
injured her fellow disciples.

00:18:44.700 --> 00:18:45.980 line:80%
That's outright treachery.

00:18:46.810 --> 00:18:47.740 line:80%
Poor Ning

00:18:48.610 --> 00:18:49.740 line:80%
fainted who knows how many times.

00:18:51.180 --> 00:18:52.220 line:80%
I'll go check on Zhou.

00:19:12.020 --> 00:19:12.980 line:80%
I never thought

00:19:14.890 --> 00:19:15.730 line:80%
Zhao

00:19:17.290 --> 00:19:18.850 line:80%
would follow Pingshu's path.

00:19:19.890 --> 00:19:21.180 line:80%
Li Min coated the silver needles

00:19:21.700 --> 00:19:22.570 line:80%
with Cold Spirit Powder.

00:19:23.460 --> 00:19:24.740 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is as good as dead.

00:19:34.430 --> 00:19:35.340 line:80%
Look.

00:19:35.340 --> 00:19:36.680 line:80%
- How terrifying.
- Look at her.

00:20:08.180 --> 00:20:10.810 line:80%
(He is in fine silks, but has
callused fingertips.)

00:20:11.220 --> 00:20:12.330 line:80%
(He is an abacus man.)

00:20:13.090 --> 00:20:14.980 line:80%
(A hard-working man should not be robbed.)

00:20:21.420 --> 00:20:23.090 line:80%
(This one lives in luxury,)

00:20:23.090 --> 00:20:24.780 line:80%
(yet treats her maid well.)

00:20:25.700 --> 00:20:29.500 line:80%
(Not evil, I can't rob her either.)

00:20:57.980 --> 00:20:59.740 line:80%
Luoying Valley

00:20:59.740 --> 00:21:01.940 line:80%
truly breeds demonesses.

00:21:02.810 --> 00:21:04.660 line:80%
Cai Zhao betrayed her master and sect,

00:21:04.660 --> 00:21:05.740 line:80%
shameless.

00:21:05.740 --> 00:21:06.700 line:80%
If I see her,

00:21:06.700 --> 00:21:08.330 line:80%
I'll avenge Beichen's disciples.

00:21:09.290 --> 00:21:10.610 line:80%
Lord Cai and his wife are pitiful.

00:21:11.460 --> 00:21:13.980 line:80%
Her parents failed to raise her,
that's their karma.

00:21:14.570 --> 00:21:16.020 line:80%
But Lord Qi

00:21:16.020 --> 00:21:18.780 line:80%
trusted her for her mother's sake,

00:21:18.780 --> 00:21:19.980 line:80%
even vouched for her.

00:21:20.940 --> 00:21:22.050 line:80%
Trust misplaced.

00:22:07.290 --> 00:22:08.850 line:80%
You must drink it.

00:22:30.370 --> 00:22:31.460 line:80%
When you recover,

00:22:32.290 --> 00:22:33.890 line:80%
I'll make you smiley

00:22:34.610 --> 00:22:36.420 line:80%
so the medicine won't taste bitter.

00:22:47.890 --> 00:22:48.730 line:80%
Did you know?

00:22:50.180 --> 00:22:53.090 line:80%
In Luoying Valley, besides peach blossoms

00:22:53.740 --> 00:22:54.610 line:80%
and wontons,

00:22:55.570 --> 00:22:56.500 line:80%
our porridge

00:22:57.290 --> 00:22:58.290 line:80%
is famous too.

00:22:59.660 --> 00:23:02.810 line:80%
A couple runs the shop at the alley entrance,

00:23:04.780 --> 00:23:07.940 line:80%
their chicken chestnut porridge is soft

00:23:08.330 --> 00:23:09.420 line:80%
and fragrant.

00:23:14.850 --> 00:23:16.120 line:80%
When I was five,

00:23:17.090 --> 00:23:18.050 line:80%
my aunt was seriously ill.

00:23:18.850 --> 00:23:19.810 line:80%
I sneaked out

00:23:20.220 --> 00:23:22.290 line:80%
with a jar to buy her porridge.

00:23:24.530 --> 00:23:26.740 line:80%
The shopkeeper was kind,

00:23:28.290 --> 00:23:29.980 line:80%
though I had no money,

00:23:30.810 --> 00:23:33.370 line:80%
she filled it anyway.

00:23:43.180 --> 00:23:45.290 line:80%
But I was too small;

00:23:48.810 --> 00:23:51.460 line:80%
the jar grew heavier with every step.

00:23:53.740 --> 00:23:54.890 line:80%
The alley

00:23:56.890 --> 00:23:58.780 line:80%
felt endless.

00:24:00.810 --> 00:24:02.530 line:80%
I was exhausted.

00:24:03.500 --> 00:24:05.290 line:80%
Just as I reached home,

00:24:07.290 --> 00:24:08.570 line:80%
I tripped.

00:24:10.610 --> 00:24:12.020 line:80%
The jar shattered.

00:24:13.700 --> 00:24:15.130 line:80%
The porridge spilled everywhere.

00:24:31.780 --> 00:24:32.620 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:24:34.570 --> 00:24:35.660 line:80%
for you,

00:24:37.500 --> 00:24:38.850 line:80%
I hurt my master,

00:24:41.130 --> 00:24:42.610 line:80%
my parents,

00:24:46.220 --> 00:24:47.740 line:80%
and Uncle Zhou.

00:24:48.330 --> 00:24:49.890 line:80%
I did all that.

00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:52.420 line:80%
If you die,

00:24:53.290 --> 00:24:54.370 line:80%
what does that make me?

00:24:56.570 --> 00:24:58.290 line:80%
When my parents sent me to the sect,

00:24:58.980 --> 00:25:00.370 line:80%
they warned me again and again...

00:25:01.370 --> 00:25:03.130 line:80%
be obedient, never

00:25:03.890 --> 00:25:05.740 line:80%
become a demoness.

00:25:10.570 --> 00:25:12.020 line:80%
Yet here I am.

00:25:14.610 --> 00:25:15.810 line:80%
Here I am.

00:25:22.500 --> 00:25:23.890 line:80%
I miss home.

00:25:25.940 --> 00:25:26.940 line:80%
In a few months,

00:25:27.810 --> 00:25:29.980 line:80%
the tri-colored peach blossoms will bloom.

00:25:38.050 --> 00:25:39.890 line:80%
Our valley has flowers all year...

00:25:40.810 --> 00:25:42.660 line:80%
spring peaches,

00:25:42.660 --> 00:25:44.050 line:80%
summer lotuses,

00:25:44.780 --> 00:25:46.180 line:80%
autumn chrysanthemums,

00:25:46.940 --> 00:25:48.130 line:80%
winter plums.

00:25:49.220 --> 00:25:50.290 line:80%
One day,

00:25:55.370 --> 00:25:57.220 line:80%
I want to show you all of it.

00:26:02.530 --> 00:26:03.370 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:26:08.980 --> 00:26:10.090 line:80%
for me,

00:26:13.810 --> 00:26:15.290 line:80%
you must live.

00:26:32.420 --> 00:26:33.500 line:80%
How is it, Fengchi?

00:26:33.500 --> 00:26:34.460 line:80%
Any news of Zhao?

00:26:34.890 --> 00:26:36.410 line:80%
Someone who betrays her sect

00:26:36.700 --> 00:26:38.050 line:80%
shouldn't return.

00:26:38.850 --> 00:26:41.050 line:80%
It's not that severe.

00:26:41.050 --> 00:26:43.570 line:80%
Master and Uncle Li weren't badly hurt.

00:26:43.570 --> 00:26:45.130 line:80%
What about their hearts?

00:26:45.740 --> 00:26:46.740 line:80%
Father adored Cai Zhao.

00:26:46.740 --> 00:26:48.610 line:80%
Yet she plotted against her own.

00:26:48.610 --> 00:26:49.810 line:80%
How heartbroken he must be?

00:26:50.570 --> 00:26:51.850 line:80%
I even tried to help her.

00:26:52.780 --> 00:26:53.620 line:80%
By the way,

00:26:53.980 --> 00:26:55.980 line:80%
where did she get the Chaos Needles
and gunpowder?

00:26:56.810 --> 00:26:58.460 line:80%
Weren't they locked in the armory?

00:26:59.890 --> 00:27:00.730 line:80%
Zhao,

00:27:01.050 --> 00:27:02.180 line:80%
I brought everything useful

00:27:02.180 --> 00:27:03.220 line:80%
from the armory.

00:27:11.610 --> 00:27:12.450 line:80%
Well,

00:27:12.660 --> 00:27:13.740 line:80%
Uncle Lei asked me to deliver medicine.

00:27:13.980 --> 00:27:14.820 line:80%
I have to go.

00:27:15.290 --> 00:27:16.180 line:80%
Did I do wrong?

00:27:16.180 --> 00:27:17.020 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:27:17.810 --> 00:27:19.740 line:80%
God of Wealth, Guanyin,

00:27:19.740 --> 00:27:21.660 line:80%
please keep her safe.

00:27:22.020 --> 00:27:23.610 line:80%
Please, please.

00:27:28.530 --> 00:27:29.700 line:80%
This is Zhao's?

00:27:33.020 --> 00:27:33.940 line:80%
Let me see.

00:27:37.090 --> 00:27:39.020 line:80%
The town connects in all directions,

00:27:39.020 --> 00:27:39.980 line:80%
and there was no witness.

00:27:40.940 --> 00:27:42.420 line:80%
There are no trace

00:27:42.420 --> 00:27:44.050 line:80%
of Mu Qingyan or Cai Zhao.

00:27:44.980 --> 00:27:46.660 line:80%
The Six Sects and Nie Zhe are hunting them.

00:27:47.310 --> 00:27:49.300 line:80%
Hiding deep in the mountains would be safer.

00:27:50.020 --> 00:27:51.290 line:80%
Why risk a town?

00:27:51.740 --> 00:27:53.080 line:80%
She went to a clinic,

00:27:53.530 --> 00:27:54.370 line:80%
bought snow lotus.

00:27:54.700 --> 00:27:55.540 line:80%
Snow lotus?

00:27:56.370 --> 00:27:58.460 line:80%
Isn't that for detoxifying?

00:27:59.020 --> 00:28:00.370 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is injured.

00:28:01.460 --> 00:28:02.500 line:80%
They can't go far.

00:28:03.020 --> 00:28:04.220 line:80%
I've sent carrier pigeons

00:28:04.940 --> 00:28:06.890 line:80%
to every sect and wandering knight.

00:28:07.370 --> 00:28:09.420 line:80%
Soon we'll have

00:28:09.420 --> 00:28:10.700 line:80%
their trail.

00:28:11.850 --> 00:28:12.780 line:80%
Master,

00:28:12.780 --> 00:28:13.820 line:80%
let me go myself.

00:28:18.260 --> 00:28:21.820 line:80%
(Past and Future Glory)

00:28:21.850 --> 00:28:22.690 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:23.820 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:28:23.940 --> 00:28:24.780 line:80%
Wait for me.

00:28:29.180 --> 00:28:30.220 line:80%
Don't blame me

00:28:30.220 --> 00:28:31.290 line:80%
for stopping you earlier.

00:28:31.740 --> 00:28:34.050 line:80%
Who knew that girl would strike so ruthlessly?

00:28:35.290 --> 00:28:37.020 line:80%
Now we take it step by step.

00:28:37.020 --> 00:28:37.890 line:80%
She's sentimental.

00:28:39.050 --> 00:28:40.090 line:80%
She owes Mu Qingyan

00:28:40.530 --> 00:28:42.180 line:80%
so she won't let him die.

00:28:42.810 --> 00:28:43.810 line:80%
Once he heals,

00:28:43.810 --> 00:28:45.370 line:80%
she'll return.

00:28:45.370 --> 00:28:46.740 line:80%
If you were so certain,

00:28:46.740 --> 00:28:48.610 line:80%
you wouldn't volunteer to chase her.

00:28:48.610 --> 00:28:51.130 line:80%
She acts without rules,

00:28:51.130 --> 00:28:52.020 line:80%
and that Mu boy

00:28:52.020 --> 00:28:53.700 line:80%
is as handsome as you.

00:28:53.700 --> 00:28:55.220 line:80%
She might never

00:28:55.220 --> 00:28:56.530 line:80%
come back.

00:28:57.500 --> 00:29:00.090 line:80%
Don't listen to your mother.

00:29:00.090 --> 00:29:02.220 line:80%
Life is short,

00:29:02.220 --> 00:29:03.660 line:80%
you should just

00:29:03.660 --> 00:29:04.940 line:80%
do as you please.

00:29:07.290 --> 00:29:08.130 line:80%
Win her back if you must.

00:29:09.290 --> 00:29:10.330 line:80%
There's nothing shameful.

00:29:17.850 --> 00:29:19.090 line:80%
Good boy.

00:29:30.220 --> 00:29:31.060 line:80%
Zhao.

00:29:32.500 --> 00:29:33.340 line:80%
You're awake.

00:29:50.610 --> 00:29:51.890 line:80%
The poison's stable now.

00:29:52.850 --> 00:29:53.690 line:80%
I thought

00:29:54.850 --> 00:29:55.780 line:80%
you'd gone home.

00:29:56.180 --> 00:29:57.090 line:80%
How could I

00:29:57.980 --> 00:29:58.850 line:80%
leave you like this?

00:30:00.020 --> 00:30:01.330 line:80%
Taste the porridge later.

00:30:01.330 --> 00:30:02.210 line:80%
My aunt said

00:30:02.210 --> 00:30:03.290 line:80%
I was as good as the shop.

00:30:06.780 --> 00:30:07.810 line:80%
I heard everything,

00:30:10.290 --> 00:30:11.330 line:80%
about Luoying Valley.

00:30:13.420 --> 00:30:15.610 line:80%
Was I foolish as a child?

00:30:18.090 --> 00:30:19.810 line:80%
I like your childhood stories.

00:30:20.810 --> 00:30:22.300 line:80%
Your home sounds

00:30:23.530 --> 00:30:24.890 line:80%
whole and bright,

00:30:25.660 --> 00:30:27.020 line:80%
just thinking of it brings joy.

00:30:29.660 --> 00:30:30.660 line:80%
Unlike mine.

00:30:31.330 --> 00:30:32.500 line:80%
If you like,

00:30:33.530 --> 00:30:34.850 line:80%
I'll share half of my childhood with you.

00:30:35.460 --> 00:30:36.780 line:80%
Then when you remember it,

00:30:37.290 --> 00:30:38.780 line:80%
you'll feel joy too.

00:30:47.850 --> 00:30:48.690 line:80%
Careful.

00:30:48.980 --> 00:30:50.850 line:80%
Li Min poisoned the needles.

00:30:51.570 --> 00:30:52.700 line:80%
He meant to kill me.

00:30:53.290 --> 00:30:54.570 line:80%
Whoever applied the poison,

00:30:55.940 --> 00:30:57.500 line:80%
the executioner must know.

00:30:58.130 --> 00:30:59.660 line:80%
Uncle Li?

00:31:00.420 --> 00:31:02.020 line:80%
He's always been fair.

00:31:02.500 --> 00:31:03.420 line:80%
He and Master...

00:31:46.020 --> 00:31:46.860 line:80%
Zhao.

00:31:48.780 --> 00:31:49.620 line:80%
Let's

00:31:52.290 --> 00:31:53.700 line:80%
rely on each other from now on.

00:31:57.090 --> 00:31:58.460 line:80%
Let's find somewhere quiet

00:31:59.130 --> 00:31:59.980 line:80%
and leave the martial world.

00:32:01.940 --> 00:32:02.780 line:80%
Okay?

00:32:48.570 --> 00:32:49.740 line:80%
(Zhao.)

00:32:58.050 --> 00:32:59.050 line:80%
It's been so long,

00:33:00.130 --> 00:33:01.940 line:80%
Mu Qingyan still hasn't been found.

00:33:02.610 --> 00:33:04.740 line:80%
Shangguan and You Guanyue

00:33:05.220 --> 00:33:06.370 line:80%
may not be trying hard.

00:33:07.220 --> 00:33:08.530 line:80%
They surrendered

00:33:09.020 --> 00:33:10.850 line:80%
only because they thought

00:33:11.330 --> 00:33:12.570 line:80%
Mu Qingyan would die after capture.

00:33:13.460 --> 00:33:14.300 line:80%
Who knew

00:33:14.460 --> 00:33:15.980 line:80%
the Six Sects

00:33:16.420 --> 00:33:17.660 line:80%
would lose him

00:33:17.980 --> 00:33:19.020 line:80%
at the execution ground?

00:33:19.610 --> 00:33:21.220 line:80%
If he lives,

00:33:21.780 --> 00:33:22.740 line:80%
I'm afraid

00:33:23.890 --> 00:33:26.020 line:80%
those two will waver.

00:33:26.780 --> 00:33:27.620 line:80%
Elder Hu,

00:33:27.810 --> 00:33:29.420 line:80%
go deal with it.

00:33:30.530 --> 00:33:31.740 line:80%
If they're still colluding

00:33:31.740 --> 00:33:33.290 line:80%
with Mu Qingyan,

00:33:34.530 --> 00:33:36.050 line:80%
eliminate them.

00:33:36.050 --> 00:33:36.890 line:80%
Yes.

00:33:53.370 --> 00:33:54.850 line:80%
The Hanhai Mountains are ahead.

00:33:55.740 --> 00:33:56.940 line:80%
Rest tonight.

00:34:07.050 --> 00:34:08.220 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:34:08.220 --> 00:34:09.140 line:80%
clever as you are,

00:34:10.290 --> 00:34:11.130 line:80%
you must know

00:34:12.220 --> 00:34:13.330 line:80%
I fear not just the dark,

00:34:13.970 --> 00:34:15.060 line:80%
but sleeping alone.

00:34:47.930 --> 00:34:48.780 line:80%
So beautiful.

00:35:04.890 --> 00:35:06.890 line:80%
A foreign moon can't

00:35:08.100 --> 00:35:10.100 line:80%
outshine the lamp of home.

00:35:10.970 --> 00:35:13.410 line:80%
I know you miss home.

00:35:48.930 --> 00:35:49.770 line:80%
You miss

00:35:52.410 --> 00:35:53.700 line:80%
your valley,

00:35:55.740 --> 00:35:56.810 line:80%
your parents,

00:35:59.370 --> 00:36:00.220 line:80%
your brother.

00:36:21.780 --> 00:36:22.620 line:80%
Zhao,

00:36:25.140 --> 00:36:25.980 line:80%
trust me.

00:36:30.290 --> 00:36:31.330 line:80%
You will go back.

00:37:16.641 --> 00:37:27.301 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:37:46.061 --> 00:37:50.471 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:37:51.036 --> 00:37:55.651 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:37:55.991 --> 00:38:00.556 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:38:01.081 --> 00:38:05.381 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:38:08.326 --> 00:38:13.026 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:13.551 --> 00:38:17.841 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:18.501 --> 00:38:22.531 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:38:22.846 --> 00:38:27.971 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:38:28.546 --> 00:38:33.356 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:33.571 --> 00:38:37.741 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:38.466 --> 00:38:42.401 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:42.901 --> 00:38:48.176 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:39:10.906 --> 00:39:16.036 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:16.401 --> 00:39:20.771 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:21.036 --> 00:39:25.166 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:25.351 --> 00:39:30.926 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪